is is your charger."> <span data-kids="This is your notebook." data-adults="This is your charger.">This is your notebook.</span></label></div><div class="prompt-card"><label><input type="checkbox" data-obs data-kids="It is his book." data-adults="It is his coffee mug."> <span data-kids="It is his book." data-adults="It is his coffee mug.">It is his book.</span></label></div><div class="prompt-card"><label><input type="checkbox" data-obs data-kids="It is her pencil." data-adults="It is her notebook."> <span data-kids="It is her pencil." data-adults="It is her notebook.">It is her pencil.</span></label></div><div class="prompt-card"><label><input type="checkbox" data-obs data-kids="These are our books." data-adults="These are our documents."> <span data-kids="These are our books." data-adults="These are our documents.">These are our books.</span></label></div><div class="prompt-card"><label><input type="checkbox" data-obs data-kids="These are their toys." data-adults="These are their keys."> <span data-kids="These are their toys." data-adults="These are their keys.">These are their toys.</span></label></div><div class="prompt-card"><label><input type="checkbox" data-obs data-kids="Is this your pen?" data-adults="Is this your phone?"> <span data-kids="Is this your pen?" data-adults="Is this your phone?">Is this your pen?</span></label></div><div class="prompt-card"><label><input type="checkbox" data-obs data-kids="Is it his football?" data-adults="Is it her pen?"> <span data-kids="Is it his football?" data-adults="Is it her pen?">Is it his football?</span></label></div></div><div class="block-nav"><a class="btn primary" href="#vocab">Next: vocabulary</a></div></section>

